io.sphere.sdk.channels

Interface Channel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CreationTimestamped, DefaultModel<Channel>, DefaultModelView<Channel>, Identifiable<Channel>, Referenceable<Channel>, Timestamped, Versioned<Channel>

    public interface Channel
extends DefaultModel<Channel>
    Channels represent a source or destination of different entities.

    Operations:

    • Create a channel with ChannelCreateCommand.
    • Fetch a channel by key with ChannelByKeyFetch.
    • Query a channel with ChannelQuery.
    • Delete a channel with ChannelDeleteCommand.
